title: Fantastic 2 BR 1 BA Townhome For Rent
posting_body: ['81 Orme St E #2 Saint Paul, MN  55118', '$1350.00 / Month', '---------------------------', 'Interested in this property?', 'Reply to this listing for more information.', '---------------------------', 'Property Details:', '2 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS', 'Fantastic 2 Bedroom 1 Bath Townhome.', 'Just a half block off of Robert Street and just south of Butler, you can literally walk to everything you need, or just a 5 minute bus ride to downtown St Paul!', "Walgreens, Caribou, Dunkin, Great Moon Buffet, Sarpino's, McDonalds, Dairy Queen, Little Caesar's, Firestone, O'Reilly, T-Mobile, Taco Libre, Dollar Tree, Micho Love, are all within one block!Everything about this place is awesome.", 'It very nice hardwood floors, in the living room and separate dining room, and a very functional and updated kitchen, all found on the first floor.', 'Upstairs there are 2 bedrooms with ample closet space and a full bathroom.', 'PLUS, there is a full basement with your own washer and dryer and TONS of storage available.', 'A long term lease is preferred as expressed in our rental rates.1 Year Lease - $1,500/mo2 Year Lease - $1,450/', 'mo3 Year Lease - $1,350/moOne small dog (under 20 lbs) OR one cat permitted, but NOT BOTH.', 'Pet rent is $50/mo for the term of the lease.', '***No Pets Allowed***', 'Property Type:', 'Townhouse', 'Lease Terms:', '$1350.00/Month', '$1350.00 Deposit', 'Lease Length:', 'One Year', 'Available:', '08/12/2022', 'Unit Amenities:', 'Dryer', 'Microwave', 'Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Washer', 'Building Amenities:', 'Cable Ready', 'Washer Dryer Hookups', 'Lawn', 'Off Street Parking', '---------------------------', 'Interested in this property?', 'Reply to this listing for more information.']
